body_html: @SPLNatho I've been able to temporarily work around the problem by invoking an inference by executing bash commands in Java (Using DefaultExecutor and CommandLine) to kick off the inference instead of using the TensorFlow API, and parsing the output. It's hacky, but it at least side steps the problem for now.
